Rihanna has been confirmed as a performer at the Abu Dhabi Grand Prix on 27 November.She will be closing the event and is expected to arrive the day before.At the same time, insiders have told TshisaLIVE that Drake is also going to be in Abu Dhabi on the very same weekend to perform at a private party."It's a big secret but Drake will be here on the same weekend as Rihanna."There has also been speculation that he could be one of the surprise acts at the Grand Prix, with the official website saying two acts are yet to be announced.Drake and Riri in the same pace at the same time? Coincidence? Maybe. Considering the two just got together, had a supposedly messy breakup and are rumoured to be chatting again, we reckon a love fest in Abu Dhabi is totes on the cards.Watch this space.